OL,6,FThe death of a 71-year-old Parc Prison
OL,7,Finmate is to be investigated by the
OL,8,FPrisons and Probation Ombudsman.
OL,10,FThe Bridgend prison's operators, G4S,
OL,11,Fsay Robert Royan died on Wednesday, 5
OL,12,FJune.
OL,14,FHe had been a hospital inpatient since
OL,15,F29 April.
OL,17,FA HMP Parc spokesperson said: "Mr
OL,18,FRobert Royan passed away on Wednesday,
OL,19,F5 June, 2024. His next of kin have
OL,20,Fbeen informed and our thoughts are
OL,21,Fwith his family and friends.
